                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "The ia32-libs package in precise exists only to provide backwards-compatibility for packages which depend on it. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": " Wine should not be using ia32-libs for building in precise.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
            "name": "vorlon", 
            "email": "vorlon"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2012-03-03 00:19:18", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "So where should wine get the 32 bit GLU dev libraries from?\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Normally I'd expect it to be able to install libglu1-mesa-dev:i386 for this, but a) it doesn't appear in the repositories, and b) it conflicts with libglu1-mesa-dev.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }
            ], 
            "name": "rockorequin", 
            "email": "rockorequin"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2012-03-03 00:27:16", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Can I add an \"affects mesa\" to this bug with a \"new\" status? ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "The core problem remains, which is that Precise does not provide 32-bit GLU dev libraries on an amd64 platform. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Or should I open another bug?\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
            "name": "rockorequin", 
            "email": "rockorequin"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2012-03-03 00:40:26", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "On Sat, Mar 03, 2012 at 12:19:18AM -0000, Rocko wrote:\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "> So where should wine get the 32 bit GLU dev libraries from?\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "It shouldn't. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": " wine needs to support building the 64-bit components on an amd64 buildd, the 32-bit components on a 32-bit buildd, and stitching them up together afterwards using binary package dependencies.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
